itemDescription: English rugby league and association footballer (1899-1974)

wikipedia_page.main: Thomas Patrick Magee (6 May 1899 – May 1974) was an English professional footballer who played as a wing half. He made more than 400 appearances during his 15 years at West Bromwich Albion. He also won five England caps.

response: * Tommy Magee (1899 in Widnes – 1974) footballer who made over 400 appearances for West Bromwich Albion F.C.
